ent and cover the configuration requirements of other non-microservices\n\n\n### installation \n\n```bash\nnpm install @byted-service/tcc-general --registry=http://bnpm.byted.org\n```\n\n### config options\n\n```ts\ninterface Options {\n    // serviceName\n    serviceName: string;\n    // cluster, default is `default`\n    cluster?: string;\n    // cache time, unit is ms , minimum is 3000ms, default is 6000ms\n    cacheTime?: number;\n    // timeout for get config from remote when cache is expired.\n    getTimeout?: number;\n}\n```\n\n### quick start\n\n```ts\nimport TccGeneral from '@byted-service/tcc-general';\n\n(async function test() {\n    const tccGeneral = TccGeneral.create({\n        serviceName: '<serviceName>'\n    });\n\n    let res;\n    try {\n        // normal config node, watch out the exception that throw by sdk\n        res = await tccGeneral.get('<nodeName>');\n        console.log('getNode res: ', res);\n    } catch (error) {\n        if (error.code === TccErrorCode.errKeyNotFound) {\n            console.log('[tcc-general] key not found, error: ', error);\n        } else {\n            console.log('[tcc-general] get error : ', error);\n        }\n    }\n\n    try {\n        // group config node\n        res = await tccGeneral.getGroupKey('<nodeName>', '<key>');\n        console.log('getGroupKey res: ', res);\n    } catch (error) {\n        if (error.code === TccErrorCode.errKeyNotFound) {\n            console.log('[tcc-general] key not found, error: ', error);\n        } else {\n            console.log('[tcc-general] getGroupKey error : ', error);\n        }\n    }\n})().then(() => {});\n```\n","name":"@byted-service/tcc-general","dist":{"integrity":"sha512-ht3Er/ty4fo3N8FpvJUhIzmncrYbHyvo4dBu34JfccfNyBEMcvl/DB7CF9LPpsxrrcKpRH9DBHcuK3I+BytvTw==","shasum":"b1706002be44654488068d2f0a6b8b5b2d7d844c","tarball":"https://bnpm.byted.org/@byted-service/tcc-general/-/tcc-general-1.0.6.tgz"},"license":"ISC","author":{"name":"sunjie"},"description":"> [TCC ge